  <h1 class="gd-h1">How Fit Do You Need to Be for Heliskiing?</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">You do not need to be an elite athlete to heliski &mdash; but powder skiing all day is genuinely demanding, and good fitness transforms how much you enjoy it and how safe you are. This honest guide explains why fitness matters, what to train and how to prepare over eight to twelve weeks. When you are ready, explore our <a href="/packages">packages</a> and heliskiing in <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
